{"tid":101162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump安插「列寧主義者」入國家安全最高級別會議","createTime":"2017-01-30T15:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T16:12:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc7ea14c11a7f19ecaf4fecb49a5ff07df532b6","tid":101162,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170130/large/30wb17p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170130%2Flarge%2F30wb17p.jpg&h=3882a457&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n特朗普與特恩布爾通電話時，班農（右）與國家安全顧問弗林在旁。美聯社 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普改組國安會　安插親信 <br />\n<br />\n備忘則指示重組白宮國家安全委員會和國土安全委員會，稱要加強美國對網絡安全的應變能力，特別安插總統首席智囊班農入國安會最高級別的定期會議，跟國務卿和國防部長看齊，顯示班農的地位更上一層樓。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170130/19912755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170130%2F19912755&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=845043d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170130%2F19912755&h=e56ff2cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170130/19912755</a> <br />\n<br />\nSteve Bannon接受媒體訪問時曾說自己是「列寧主義者」，因為「列寧想要摧毀國家體制，我的目的也是如此。我想要推倒一切，摧毀今日所有的建制。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/steve-bannon-will-lead-trumps-white-house\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-desk%2Fsteve-bannon-will-lead-trumps-white-house&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=754f162a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/steve-bannon-will-lead-trumps-white-house</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想推倒一切，摧毀所有建制既人 <br />\n地位同國務卿國防部長看齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22abaf70cdfa3f5b993638c535916716ff9040d","tid":101162,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}